@startuml
title Fiat-Shamir with Aborts (lattice identification, non-interactive)
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

participant "Signer\n(knows s1, s2)" as P
participant "Hash H\n(challenge oracle)" as H
participant "Verifier\n(knows A, t)" as V

== Commitment ==
P -> P : sample mask y (small)
P -> P : w = A y\nw1 = HighBits(w)

== Challenge (derived, not interactive) ==
P -> H : mu || w1
H --> P : c~  then  c = SampleInBall(c~)

== Response ==
P -> P : z = y + c*s1
note right of P
  Reject and restart if
  ||z|| >= gamma1 - beta
  or ||r0|| >= gamma2 - beta
end note
P -> V : sigma = (c~, z, h)

== Check ==
V -> V : w'1 from A z - c*t1*2^d + hint
V -> V : accept iff\n||z|| < gamma1 - beta\nand c~ = H(mu || w'1)
@enduml
